---
title: Spiced Middle Eastern Double Lamb Rump with Sumac Potato Wedges & Turnip Salad
description: A sumptuous lamb feast with a Middle Eastern twist. This tender lamb rump is spiced with chermoula, then paired with crispy sumac wedges
and a crunchy turnip salad. Don’t forget to rest your lamb for 10 minutes after cooking for the perfect slices that are blushing and moist.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ab655e16ef9662eb86ecf4-4698db88.jpeg
